        =======
        History
        =======
        
        0.4.0 (2018-04-23)
        ------------------
        
        * Python 2.7 support on Windows. Python3 not yet supported on Windows.
        
        0.3.0
        -----
        
        * run_process() renamed to run()
        * Python3 compatibility fixes
        
        0.2.0 (2018-03-12)
        ------------------
        
        * Procrunner is now Python3 3.3-3.6 compatible.
        
        0.1.0 (2018-03-12)
        ------------------
        
        * First release on PyPI.
        
